Merge feature/phase3-optimizations into main

Combines Phase 1-3 performance optimizations:
- Granular vendor chunk splitting (react/router/query/editor/mermaid/dnd)
- Eager/lazy page split for faster initial load
- Enhanced API key cache (10min TTL, size-capped at 10k entries)
- Extended DB pool idle_timeout to 300s for serverless envs
- Compression upgrade to ^1.8.1
- Better auth.ts with inline cache and full key fields
